channel.title: Hah Bah Scape V2 - Need help with base server
channel.description:
Well I'm getting ready to start Hah Bah Scape V2, and am going to start with a fresh base server just for fun, lol. I need some suggestions on a few servers I could use though... Please list a server or two that you think would make a good base server...
Things I want: A few premade shops (this makes it easy to add/remove items to them an move them around) A decent training place (I really dont feel like making a new one) Working Specs Working Weapon emotes Working Bow emotes (I specified this because in most servers, the crystal bow emote is shit) Working log out timer (must wait 10 seconds after combat) Working teleports (even if they are edited, I can change them back)
Things I would REALLY enjoy, but arent a must: Skillcape Emotes (0mg 5k1llc4p3 3m0t3z h4x!) Godsword Minigame any other minigames
